data.description: PRICED TO SELL. Move in and enjoy this beautiful home in this prestigious community of Estrella. Fully remodeled. Features modern tones, wood looking ceramic tile, white shaker cabinets, granite counters, kitchen pantry, stainless steel appliances, wine fridge and ceiling fans throughout. Surround sound in several rooms and patio. Home is breathtaking inside and out. Open office/dining room. Formal living room with shiplap built in accent wall with a gas insert fp and glass rocks. Large extra room can be a 4 bedroom or large office/craft or exercise room. Closet can be added. Backyard is resort with everything to enjoy for entertaining. Gas outdoor fireplace, covered gazebo, built in Blackstone, splash pad and synthetic grass. Come enjoy! Decorate for the holidays. Leased Solar just added SAVE, SAVE, SAVE!!! No more high APS Bills
